title: For Sale:  Springfield Armory TRP 1911 .45ACP w/ Night Sights - Customized
postcontent: Up for sale is my customized Springfield Armory TRP 1911. This pistol is in perfect condition (less than 1,000 rounds through it), has been extremely well-maintained, and features a number of custom modifications that make it a dream for the true 1911 enthusiast. I have been holding onto this pistol in the hopes that I would find the time to get to the range and enjoy it, but my schedule just won't allow it these days, so I'd like to see it go to someone who will enjoy and appreciate it.The Springfield TRP (Tactical Response Pistol) is one of the best 1911s on the market. It features a forged carbon steel national match frame and slide with a black Armory Kote finish, a stainless steel match grade barrel, a 4.5-5 lb trigger pull, low-profile 3-dot Tritium night sights, black/grey G10 grips, and 2 stainless steel 7-round .45ACP magazines with slam pads. While the factory TRP is an excellent firearm, this particular pistol has been modified to reduce recoil, increase accuracy, improve handling, and reduce wear that results from normal use. All custom machine work was performed by an experienced and reputable 1911 gunsmith (Jimmy Mitchell of Mitchell Custom Guns in Breckenridge, TX). Each part was checked, machined, and tested for this specific pistol, ensuring perfect fit and performance. Here is a list of improvements and high-quality aftermarket parts that have been added to this pistol:- EGW 1-piece tungsten full-length guide rod- Custom stainless steel short flat trigger- SVI reverse recoil spring plug (spring tunnel/dust cover of slide has been machined to fit this plug)- 16 lb. Wolff recoil spring- EGW flat-bottom firing pin stop- Smith & Alexander mag guide mainspring housing (20 LPI checkering)- 19 lb. Ed Brown mainspring- Wilson Combat Factory Plus mainspring internals (cap, retainer, and pin)- Ed Brown steel firing pin- Wolff Extra Power firing pin spring- "1/4 notch" removed from hammer- Wilson Combat Bullet Proof Tactical thumb safety (single-sided safety)- Wilson Combat Factory Plus hammer and sear pins- Wilson Combat Bullet Proof semi-extended slide release- Wilson Combat Bullet Proof Tactical mag release- VZ Elite Tactical Carry (ETC) G10 grips in black cherry finish I am selling this pistol with the original case, 2 magazines, gun lock, plastic holster, plastic magazine holder, and cleaning brush. You will also receive the original parts (in case you'd like to revert some of the modifications back to their factory state, to better suit the pistol to your liking). The pistol will come with 2 sets of VZ ETC G10 grips (one for use with a single-sided safety, and another for use with a double-sided safety), as well as the original black/grey G10 grips. I'm also including a really comfortable N82 Tactical IWB holster for this pistol, as well as a leather magazine holder.  If you're interested, I have a few boxes of Federal HST hollowpoint ammunition that I would be willing to sell along with the pistol for a fair price. My asking price for this pistol is $1,250 OBO.  If you are local, cash is preferred for payment.  If not, I am willing to accept PayPal.  I am not capable of accepting credit card payments because I am a private individual and not a business, and I'm not comfortable accepting any sort of personal/cashier's check.  If you are not local, I am willing to ship this firearm to your FFL via UPS Next Day Air or FedEx Priority Overnight.
